{"tid":1390252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用航拍機拍低衝突現場對前線手足同charge警有無用","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:11:45.000Z","uid":288146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3172831186f579a018ff8589c8662961d0e7cedc","tid":1390252,"uid":288146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"近呢幾次衝突警察gear明顯level up 狂出催淚彈又出射燈阻住前線記者拍攝 721開始仲要上埋橋射人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實好多時都係警察一出現/動武 示威者先會起鋼還擊 警察理應唔駛濫用暴力去清場 所以記錄住現場嘅所有片段都好重要 完整嘅就更好 可以用返嚟比較同做證<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">弱弱一問如果用航拍機喺上空影低現場 記錄低警察防線動武嘅全過程同埋點對前線手足 對之後追究警察同in case前線手足被控會唔會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>？ 本身唔熟航拍機 知道佢啲電好似唔捱得耐 見727元朗嗰次有人用 唔肯定係咪記者 有無大大可以解答下 <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候 好多人都係睇到零碎嘅片段就話前線手足係暴徒 真相真係好重要亦好需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9797d78e65d031b10ddb5e46d785a0f12eb5b2e1","tid":1390252,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"好撚貴。"},{"pid":"85531e524b0b964a02541516274e6ca36fa87bf1","tid":1390252,"uid":264324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:07:54.000Z","msg":"有似話有干擾"},{"pid":"36cc494906518f0a0851577b694ad82feff4e887","tid":1390252,"uid":288146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"Push~"},{"pid":"2346d16ce4b9abc9752695fca69821ed92f7df4d","tid":1390252,"uid":288146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"Push~"},{"pid":"0001293184f6b2eef8ef5032fa767f2216a28abf","tid":1390252,"uid":288146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96446e1af1b4dd2e50ac0a76417805c9382826c1","tid":1390252,"uid":290531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:11:14.00